Project Context:
- Micro-Unit Starter Kit (B2): 3–5 lesson mini-units for Australian teachers.
- Part of Lesson & Assessment Forge module vision.

AI Behavior:
- Use UNIT_PACK_SYSTEM from src/unit_prompts.py for Gemini generation.
- Run validate_unit_output before returning or exporting; retry up to 3 attempts.
- Australian English; practical classroom activities; no paste-ready student assessment answers.

Stack:
- client/: React + Tailwind + Vite (FBG teacher chrome)
- server/: FastAPI on port 8009
- src/: ACARA descriptor picks, generation, guardrails, DOCX/ZIP export

UI:
- Theme Auto/Light/Dark; top bar Ask button.
- App title: **Micro-Unit** (muted) + **Starter Kit** (blue).
